Discuss scientific papers!
--------------------------

Discuss scientific papers with your friends.
Follow not journals, but authors, reposts etc.
like twitter but with papers.
              do the presentation about
              open peer review, etc.



Technical info
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

we use python3, flask, werkzeug, sqlite3, gs

USERS SHOULD NOT BE ABLE TO REGISTER USERS UNDER THE NAMES:
    all, registers, and other 1-word urls...


BEFORE RUNNING, YOU SHOULD CHANGE THE SALT in papersite/config.py

